General.Name: BikeExchange Pty Ltd
General.Description: BikeExchange Limited operates online cycling marketplaces. The company's marketplaces provide a technology driven platform to connect consumers with retailers of bicycle products and accessories. It also operates bicycle retail stores; and provides bicycle logistics services. The company operates in Australia, New Zealand, Europe, North America, and Colombia. BikeExchange Limited was founded in 2007 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
